id: pm-tu71
title: "GH-457: pm health hangs during vectorization check with no output (never-block violation)"
description: "Dogfood GH-457: pm health can hang silently in the vectorization check until externally killed (reproduces with extensions disabled); gating commands must never hang. Likely same provider-probe family as GH-455 but distinct symptom (hang vs noisy failure). Duplicate check: searched health hang — no existing item."
